high_descs: Turn left and step forward to face the table.
Pick up the knife on the table.
Walk around to face the bread loaf on the opposite side of the table.
Cut the loaf of bread on the edge of the counter into slices.
Walk around the center table to face the trash can on the floor.
Place the knife in the trash can on the floor.
Walk around to face the bread loaf on the opposite side of the table.
Pick up a slice of bread on the table.
Turn around and step forward to face the fridge.
Cool the bread slice in the fridge and then remove it.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the trash can on the floor.
Place the bread slice in the trash can on the floor.
anns.task_desc: Cool a slice of bread and place it in the trash can.

high_descs: Back up, turn left and walk toward the island.
Pick up the yellow handled knife from the island.
Turn left and walk around the island and to the other side, opposite of where the knife was picked up from.
Slice the loaf of bread between the potato and bottle.
Turn to the right and walk to the trash bin on the the other side of the island.
Place the knife inside the trash bin.
Turn to the right and walk back to the bread on the other side of the island .
Pick up a slice of bread from the middle of the loaf.
Turn right and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the door, place bread inside, close door. Open the door, remove bread, close the door.
Turn right and walk to the trash bin.
Throw the bread slice into the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw a cooled slice of bread into the trash bin.

high_descs: Back up, turn to the left, go forward, turn to the left, go forward to the garbage can, turn right and go to the table where the glasses are.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that is on the table.
Turn to the left, go around the table to the other side, turn to the table where the bread and bottle of wine is.
Cut the bread just to the left of the wine into slices.
Turn to the right, go around to the other side of the table, turn to the right to the garbage can.
Put the knife in to the garbage can.
Turn around and go forward, turn to the left, go around to the other side of the table where the sliced bread is.
Pick up a slice of bread from the table.
Turn to the right, go forward to the fridge on the right.
Put the bread inside the fridge and close the door, remove the cold bread from the fridge and close the door.
Turn around and go forward to the stove, go to the left and turn right to face the garbage can.
Put the bread in to the garbage can.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife and cold bread in a garbage can.
